#. Id: 50254-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 0.0
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#. -- Condition: Who: ME, Condition: MET_TARGET_BEFORE=0, Tag: -1
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IN_MY_BUILDING=1, Tag: -1
#: 50254-rebirth.mod:0
msgid "Greetings new customer!"
msgstr "嘿新客戶!"

#. Id: 50257-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (50254-rebirth.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#: 50257-rebirth.mod:0
msgid "Welcome to Armour King!  The greatest armour shop in the world."
msgstr "歡迎來到盔甲之王! 這裏有世界上最好的盔甲."

#. Id: 50258-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 0.0
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IN_MY_BUILDING=1, Tag: -1
#: 50258-rebirth.mod:0
msgid "Armour King has the best selection in the remnants of the world"
msgstr "來盔甲之王是你最好的選擇"

#. Id: 50258-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 0.1
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IN_MY_BUILDING=1, Tag: -1
#: 50258-rebirth.mod:1
msgid "My armour is the greatest."
msgstr "我的盔甲是最幫的."

#. Id: 50258-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 0.2
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IN_MY_BUILDING=1, Tag: -1
#: 50258-rebirth.mod:2
msgid "I am Armour King"
msgstr "我是盔甲之王"

#. Id: 50258-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 0.3
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IN_MY_BUILDING=1, Tag: -1
#: 50258-rebirth.mod:3
msgid "This shop is called \"Armour King\", because the armour is the best."
msgstr "這個商店叫'盔甲之王', 因為, 它的盔甲是最好的~."

#. Id: 50258-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 0.4
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IN_MY_BUILDING=1, Tag: -1
#: 50258-rebirth.mod:4
msgid "Tell your friends that Armour King has the best armour."
msgstr "像你的朋友推薦盔甲之王把."

#. Id: 50258-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 0.5
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IN_MY_BUILDING=1, Tag: -1
#: 50258-rebirth.mod:5
msgid "Forgive me for following you, but you look like a thief."
msgstr "原諒我跟著你, 因為你看起來有點..像小偷."

#. Id: 50258-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 0.6
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IN_MY_BUILDING=1, Tag: -1
#: 50258-rebirth.mod:6
msgid ""
"I must keep my eye on you so that you are not tempted to steal such amazing "
"armour.  Ha ha."
msgstr "我必須隨時盯著你, 因為我不想平白失去這麼精美的盔甲. 哈哈."

#. Id: 50265-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 0.0
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IN_MY_BUILDING=1, Tag: -1
#: 50265-rebirth.mod:0
msgid "You cannot buy better armour anywhere in the world. "
msgstr "你在其它地方可找不到這麼好的盔甲."

#. Id: 50266-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (50265-rebirth.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#: 50266-rebirth.mod:0
msgid "I have checked.  It took me 67 years."
msgstr "我看過了. 那個花費了我67年."

#. Id: 50269-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 0.0
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IN_MY_BUILDING=1, Tag: -1
#: 50269-rebirth.mod:0
msgid ""
"I can't blame you if you try to steal my armour, because it is the best."
msgstr "就算你想偷我也能理解, 因為這盔甲實在是太精美了."

#. Id: 50269-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 0.1
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IN_MY_BUILDING=1, Tag: -1
#: 50269-rebirth.mod:1
msgid ""
"You are probably tempted to steal things, I would feel the same in your "
"position."
msgstr "我估計你想偷盔甲, 如果我是你的話我也會這樣想的."

#. Id: 50269-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 0.2
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IN_MY_BUILDING=1, Tag: -1
#: 50269-rebirth.mod:2
msgid ""
"If you feel the urge to steal, that's okay, it's a natural feeling when "
"presented with such great armour."
msgstr "如果你有想偷的衝動, 也能理解, 因為沒有人能抵擋住這麼好的裝甲的誘惑."

#. Id: 50270-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (50269-rebirth.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#: 50270-rebirth.mod:0
msgid "But I will have to kill you."
msgstr "但是我不得不殺掉你."

#. Id: 50270-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 1.1
#. -- Parent line: 0 (50269-rebirth.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#: 50270-rebirth.mod:1
msgid "I will end you though."
msgstr "之後我不得不終結你."

#. Id: 50270-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 1.2
#. -- Parent line: 0 (50269-rebirth.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#: 50270-rebirth.mod:2
msgid "Don't though."
msgstr "想都別想."

#. Id: 50271-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 0.0
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IN_MY_BUILDING=1, Tag: -1
#: 50271-rebirth.mod:0
msgid ""
"Now maybe you are thinking, \"I should kill Armour King so I can take all "
"his great armour\""
msgstr "現在你會想,\"我可以殺了盔甲之王,這樣我就可以拿到所有盔甲\""

#. Id: 50276-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (50271-rebirth.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#: 50276-rebirth.mod:0
msgid "I don't recommend this action however."
msgstr "然而我不建議你這麼做."

#. Id: 50276-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 1.1
#. -- Parent line: 0 (50271-rebirth.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#: 50276-rebirth.mod:1
msgid "You cannot.  I am deadly."
msgstr "你做不到."

#. Id: 50276-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 1.2
#. -- Parent line: 0 (50271-rebirth.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#: 50276-rebirth.mod:2
msgid "You will fail at this."
msgstr "你會栽在這個上的."

#. Id: 50277-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 0.0
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IN_MY_BUILDING=1, Tag: -1
#. -- Condition: Target Race(s): Greenlander or Hive Prince or Scorchlander
#: 50277-rebirth.mod:0
msgid ""
"Beings like yourselves are squishy and vulnerable to stabbing by pointed "
"objects."
msgstr "你們這種生物, 很容易被尖尖的東西刺傷."

#. Id: 50277-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 0.1
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IN_MY_BUILDING=1, Tag: -1
#. -- Condition: Target Race(s): Greenlander or Hive Prince or Scorchlander
#: 50277-rebirth.mod:1
msgid "Humans are weak against stabbing"
msgstr "人類是脆弱的"

#. Id: 50277-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 0.2
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IN_MY_BUILDING=1, Tag: -1
#. -- Condition: Target Race(s): Greenlander or Hive Prince or Scorchlander
#: 50277-rebirth.mod:2
msgid "Some advice:  Your soft skins are easily pierced by sharp objects."
msgstr "一點建議: 你那柔軟的身體很容易被尖銳的物體貫穿."

#. Id: 50280-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (50277-rebirth.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#: 50280-rebirth.mod:0
msgid "Overcome your weakness with armour from the Armour King"
msgstr "要克服這個缺點你就需要我的盔甲"

#. Id: 50280-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 1.1
#. -- Parent line: 0 (50277-rebirth.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#: 50280-rebirth.mod:1
msgid "Armour King has the solution."
msgstr "盔甲之王可以解決你的煩惱."

#. Id: 95999-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 0.0
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IN_MY_BUILDING=1, Tag: -1
#: 95999-rebirth.mod:0
msgid "Armour King! Armour King! Saving Lives! With Armour-ing!"
msgstr "盔甲之王! 盔甲之王! 用護甲拯救生命!"

#. Id: 96001-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 0.0
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IN_MY_BUILDING=1, Tag: -1
#: 96001-rebirth.mod:0
msgid "Do not mind the Thralls!"
msgstr "不要介意這些傭人!"

#. Id: 96013-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (96001-rebirth.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#: 96013-rebirth.mod:0
msgid "I retrieved them from the Ashlands"
msgstr "我在灰燼之島找到了他們"

#. Id: 96009-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (96013-rebirth.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#: 96009-rebirth.mod:0
msgid ""
"But do not fear! I modified them myself to make them only murderous to "
"armour thieves!"
msgstr "不必擔心! 我修改了他們, 他們隻會對想對我盔甲出手的小人攻擊!"

#. Id: 96002-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (96009-rebirth.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#: 96002-rebirth.mod:0
msgid ""
"They are much stronger than normal thralls, but don't let that scare you!"
msgstr "他們比普通的強很多, 但也不用太在意他們!"

#. Id: 96003-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (96002-rebirth.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#: 96003-rebirth.mod:0
msgid "Unless you are a thief..."
msgstr "除非(盯), 你是一個小偷...."

#. Id: 96005-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 0.0
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: IN_MY_BUILDING=1, Tag: -1
#: 96005-rebirth.mod:0
msgid ""
"Even though the Thralls have no heads, they are good at spotting thievery! "
"Oh yes!"
msgstr "沒錯! 盡管這些傭人沒有腦袋, 但是他們依然很擅長發現小偷!"

#. Id: 96007-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (96005-rebirth.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#: 96007-rebirth.mod:0
msgid ""
"I gave them special audio sensors.  In their hands.  That is how they know a "
"thief you see."
msgstr "我給了他們一個特殊的聲波傳感器. 在他們手上. 這也是他們發現小偷的方法."

#. Id: 96008-rebirth.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (96007-rebirth.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: armour king see neutral
#: 96008-rebirth.mod:0
msgid ""
"And I upgraded their armour of course.  It's the best armour in the world!"
msgstr "當然我也增強了他們的盔甲. 畢竟我可是盔甲之王!"
